Title: Constrained Differential Renormalization of Yang-Mills Theories

Authors: M. Perez-Victoria

Comments: LaTex, 13 pages with 2 ps figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B442 (1998) 315-325

We renormalize QCD to one loop in coordinate space using constraineddifferential renormalization, and show explicitly that the Slavnov-Tayloridentities are preserved by this method.